metadata.name: Fun Guy #2
metadata.description: We are The Fun Guys! Adventuring in a pack of quirky mushrooms we are accompanied by our cool snail friend. Similar to earthâ€™s critters, creatures, and humans we are roaming this wonderful planet in hopes to spark a little joy in peoples lives. Our purpose here is to not only bring a groovy energy to everyone's NFT collection, but to spread love, silliness, and a little magic. Much like humans each one of us is similar, but also different and unique in our own way.
